Rust Ecosystem Dependencies
----------------------------

This project depends on numerous open-source Rust crates, primarily licensed
under MIT and/or Apache-2.0. Key dependencies include:

- tokio - MIT License
  Asynchronous runtime for Rust
  Copyright (c) Tokio Contributors
  https://github.com/tokio-rs/tokio

- sqlx - MIT OR Apache-2.0
  Async SQL toolkit for Rust
  Copyright (c) sqlx contributors
  https://github.com/launchbadge/sqlx

- axum - MIT License
  Web framework built on tokio
  Copyright (c) 2021 Tower Contributors
  https://github.com/tokio-rs/axum

- serde - MIT OR Apache-2.0
  Serialization framework for Rust
  Copyright (c) serde-rs contributors
  https://github.com/serde-rs/serde

- pgvector-rust - Apache-2.0
  Rust client for pgvector
  Copyright (c) Andrew Kane
  https://github.com/pgvector/pgvector-rust

For a complete list of dependencies and their licenses, see:
- Cargo.lock (Rust dependencies)
- mcp-server/package-lock.json (Node.js dependencies)

